KitKat::

She was in wolf mode and ran past Drillbit. "I"LL GET THAT LITTLE 
WEASEL!!"  She ducked her head and dodged most of the flying debre 
from the grenades. She was getting mad that this fox was damaging her 
ship. She went all out in a dead run after FoxFingers. She saw him 
duk into the hole. She growled and followed, catching up to him very 
quickly.
